{"type":"question","id":2141,"title":"为何中国大陆除了Ingress之外没有别的适地性游戏？","uid":739,"topics":[],"contents":"众所周知，宝可梦GO锁区应该是公司行为。之前有开飞机玩过，但是因为这样失去了侵入式虚拟现实游戏的乐趣所以放弃了。之后不断有类似的local basic类的游戏比如侏罗纪世界，行尸走肉our world（ios），但是中国大陆的地图上是不会出现恐龙和行尸的。<br>\n<br>\n所以我很想知道：<br>\n<br>\n这类游戏的锁区（地域歧视？），是公司行为，还是与GFW的开放权限有关？<br>\n<br>\nIngress就能在地图上刷出portal，别的游戏就啥都没有。<br>\n<br>\n不过想想，反正我们连人权都没有，还能玩Ingress，真的是太棒了呢。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/7ba4a91e9180540c18a35f353b9b8d49.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/7ba4a91e9180540c18a35f353b9b8d49.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/7ba4a91e9180540c18a35f353b9b8d49.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/f577849b1e849c5a3c062f2bfbba1067.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/f577849b1e849c5a3c062f2bfbba1067.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/f577849b1e849c5a3c062f2bfbba1067.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/3cf108cecd83a9fed9d520ea7cb70ca3.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/3cf108cecd83a9fed9d520ea7cb70ca3.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/3cf108cecd83a9fed9d520ea7cb70ca3.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/943a7e54345e097c8842f61a7e7205ea.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/943a7e54345e097c8842f61a7e7205ea.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/questions/20180803/943a7e54345e097c8842f61a7e7205ea.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-08-03","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}